Specism
[[File:Fyiad.jpg|thumb|Typical specist propaganda.]]
[[File:Eng Hammer.jpg|thumb|Typical specist.]]

Specism is kind is like [[racist|racism]], except instead of being [[RAGE|hatred]] against [[niggers|a particular race]], its hatred against a particular species. Usually [[FYIAD|dragons]] hating humans. However it can also be used to denote fursecution, since furries are all sub-human.

==How to Identify a Specist==

Here is a useful list of [[typical]] specist traits that can help you identify a specist in the wild.

*Liberal use of [[FYIAD]]
*Talks about humans like Nazis talk about Jews
*[[:File:Pete burns.jpg|Stupid]], [[:File:COCAINE IS BAD FOR YOU by TR0LLHAMMEREN.jpg|fucking]], [[:File:Pony-hawk-crying-01-2007-08-04.jpg|batshit-insane]], [[:File:RoguePineapple.jpg|totally]] [[:File:EmoDarkerThanNiggers.JPG|"original"]] [[:File:Emogang.jpg|hairstyle]]
*[[Trench coat]]
*[[murder|Homicidal]]
*Has [[no life]]
*Listens to [[otherkin|Bal-Sagoth]] and [[LARP|GWAR]]
*Owns at least one [[fursuit]]
*Is [[batshit insane|batshit-fucking-insane]]

Now, while not all specists have traits 1 - 8, ALL specists have the last one, and you should point it out to them every chance you get, as most specists are oblivious to this fact.

